                <h1>Who Owns FanDuel? - Insights into Ownership</h1>
                <p>FanDuel is primarily owned by Flutter Entertainment, a global sports betting and gaming company that acquired it in 2018 through a merger with the BBC's sports betting unit. FanDuel started as a daily fantasy sports platform but has expanded into a comprehensive online sports betting and casino gaming service, serving millions of customers across the U.S.</p>
